text: Have eaten  at this subterranean restaurant twice with great service! The maki are good, as are the apps, but I would not say that anything brilliant happens in the kitchen or sushi bar. I'd like to see Hatsuhana offer some freshly made, customised desserts.

While the prices aren't great, I would count them as reasonable.  And the staff is wonderfully friendly and efficient.  Also, the portions are better than I've seen at many other places.  Worth a try!
a pretty good sushi place.. its reasonably priced and the service is fast
